			</div></section><section class="dropdown widget widget_text" aria-label=""><button type="button" id="text-3" class="title btn btn-block px-0 dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">ARCHIVES</button><div class="dropdown-menu">			<div class="textwidget"><ul><li class="jahr"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2026/">2026</a><ul class="monthlist"><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2026/01/">January</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2026/02/">February</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2026/03/">March</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2026/04/">April</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2026/05/">May</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2026/06/">June</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2026/07/">July</a></li></ul></li><li class="jahr"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/">2025</a><ul class="monthlist"><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/01/">January</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/03/">March</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/04/">April</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/05/">May</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/06/">June</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/07/">July</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/08/">August</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/09/">September</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/11/">November</a></li><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2025/12/">December</a></li></ul></li><li class="jahr"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/music/2024/">2024</a><ul class="monthlist"><li class="month"><a href="https://blogs.loc.gov/mus